reviews.text: Artistic decor with serious hi-end audio and good choice of music, giving a relaxing and comfortable dining environment.  Food and servixe are best in class.  Went on a Saturday night.  Make sure you have a reservation.
A cozy Italian restaurant in Sai Kung. Food is on average standard. It's worthwhile to spend a laid back afternoon in Sai Kung and enjoy a great view of the sea shore there.

Had lunch. The place is nice and relaxing But the food is not good at all. Over cooked chips which was soft and oily, not dubble cooked. The pork is not even pork chop. Just a very thin slice and dry. The macaroni is very soft and dry cheese. Staff are very slow and the food was very slow. The only good thing was the coffee.

A cozy little English Restaurant in Sai Kung. The food is great especially the Roasted Lamb Rack that I ordered. However I recommended to go there after work or during weekend because this is a place that you would want to have a bottle of wine with your friends😜。

A local restaurant located in a touristy area serving European Cuisine. Well known for its coffee drinks. Signature dishes include Roasted Spring Chicken, Blue Mussels in White Wine, Kurobuta Pork Loin. The restaurant has three outlets located in Kennedy Town, Tsim Sha Tsui and Sai Kung.

result.name: Gastrobox by Okapi Cafe

reviews.text: Artistic decor with serious hi-end audio and good choice of music, giving a relaxing and comfortable dining environment.  Food and servixe are best in class.  Went on a Saturday night.  Make sure you have a reservation.
A cozy Italian restaurant in Sai Kung. Food is on average standard. It's worthwhile to spend a laid back afternoon in Sai Kung and enjoy a great view of the sea shore there.

來西貢除咗食海鮮之外，其實仲有好多選擇，好似呢間充滿歐陸風情的西餐廳「Gastrobox by Okapi Cafe」🍴，係我近期試過覺得好值得推薦嘅餐廳🤗門面有幾扇深棕色的摺門，配上金色窗框，完全有自己獨特的魅力[色]店內的擺設一絲不苟，無論油畫、吊燈、裝飾，彷彿置身歐陸博物館之中，令人目不暇給🤗餐廳提供不同時段優惠，尤其是Happy Hour，酒水接近半價，我當然唔會執輸😬龍蝦🦞湯，濃濃的蝦味鮮甜無比，喝得出真材實料，還有大大塊龍蝦肉，配牛油麵包，整體賣相吸引😋Main Course選了烤西班牙🇪🇸特級黑豬扒$238和烤特級安格斯肉眼牛扒12安士$318，首先品嚐一下這個西班牙豬扒，跟平時食開的分別很大，肉質比較結實但咬下又有爽的感覺，真的與別不同[色]安格斯肉眼牛扒感覺上不至12安士，又厚又大件，絕對重質又重量，五成熟是我必然的選擇，入口肉味濃香而不膩，絕對高水準的享受😋主菜可享加$80元有龍蝦🦞半隻，決定試半隻，份量相當唔錯，肉厚彈牙，大大隻龍蝦鉗，食得輕鬆，正👍🏻甜品🍮朱古力心太軟配雪糕$68，賣相精緻，未食已經開心，甜品永遠令人感到溫暖，雖然已經有九成飽的我，馬上用另外一個胃去處理這道甜品😬
還要一提這裏服務十分貼心周到，出餐效率快而準，確是西貢的另一個好選擇👍🏻
食物味道唔錯，價錢合理，但本人食完後比較口乾
